        <p>
          BC PNP Calculator is an independent educational resource and is <strong>not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to the Government of British Columbia</strong> or any official immigration authority.
        </p>
        <p>
          The calculator and information provided on this website are for informational purposes only and should not be considered legal or immigration advice. Always consult with a licensed immigration consultant or lawyer for professional guidance.
        </p>

        <h2>Accuracy of Information</h2>
        <p>
          While we strive to provide accurate and up-to-date information, we make no warranties or representations about the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of any content on this website. Immigration policies and point systems are subject to change without notice.
        </p>

        <h2>Use of the Calculator</h2>
        <p>
          The BC PNP points calculator is a tool designed to help you estimate your score under the Skills Immigration Registration System (SIRS). The results are estimates only and do not guarantee eligibility or an invitation to apply.
        </p>
        <p>
          Your actual score may differ based on official assessment criteria applied by the BC PNP.
        </p>

        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          BC PNP Calculator shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising from:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your use of or inability to use the website</li>
          <li>Any errors or omissions in the content</li>
          <li>Decisions made based on information provided on this website</li>
          <li>Any unauthorized access to or use of our servers</li>
        </ul>

